high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white table.
Pick up the spoon behind the potato on the middle of the table.
Head right to the fridge and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the spoon on the left side of the sink, rinse it and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the left towards the silver bin on the floor next to the counter.
Open the drawer to the right of the bin, put the rinsed spoon inside and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed spoon in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the white table.
Pick up the spoon that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the fridge then turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the spoon in the left sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and take two steps then turn left and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Open the drawer under the counter top to the left of the stove and put the spoon in there then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn and go to the table.
Pick up a spoon on the table.
Turn and go to the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink.
Turn and go to the counter by the stove.
Put the spoon in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed spoon in the drawer by the stove.
